    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🦆 A Puzzle Game in Detective’s Clothing</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You solve the puzzles; Gregory solves the mystery! Every string you pull brings him one step closer to Quacking the Case!  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156700/extras/89403e14b3fcdbb68c00f1c379ac8cae.poster.avif?t=1733092633\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156700/extras/89403e14b3fcdbb68c00f1c379ac8cae.webm?t=1733092633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156700/extras/89403e14b3fcdbb68c00f1c379ac8cae.mp4?t=1733092633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🐦 Meet a Cast of Colorful Characters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the mystery deepens, new birds arrive with clues, motives, and maybe a few red herrings. Each character adds a new layer to the case; some might even throw Gregory off track! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156700/extras/2b6be8e256eb4a0e9c6cd05aa5fae2b5.poster.avif?t=1733092633\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156700/extras/2b6be8e256eb4a0e9c6cd05aa5fae2b5.webm?t=1733092633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156700/extras/2b6be8e256eb4a0e9c6cd05aa5fae2b5.mp4?t=1733092633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💡 Puzzles With a Twist</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not every pin is what it seems. From light bulbs to unexpected connections, each puzzle keeps you on your toes with clever mechanics and surprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156700/extras/40c8c41258dc71178c8aa566fe990d3b.poster.avif?t=1733092633\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156700/extras/40c8c41258dc71178c8aa566fe990d3b.webm?t=1733092633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156700/extras/40c8c41258dc71178c8aa566fe990d3b.mp4?t=1733092633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
